data.description: This beautiful spacious home on a large useable acre has all the space you need. Main floor has living, dining & family rooms, main floor office, chef's kitchen with granite counters, island, eating nook, pantry, half bath and laundry. Upstairs has a master suite w/5 piece bath, vaulted ceilings & huge walk-in closet, the other bedrooms are also huge! Back deck overlooks the peaceful backyard with a pavilion great for entertaining or hanging out at your fire pit. Small barn plus pasture is ready for pets/animals. Located in desirable Manchester close to ferry access and the sound. Tandem 3 car garage for vehicles, toys or shop space. RV parking too. Lots of room to spread out here and settled in to your new home.
